<el-select
  ref="elSelect"
  v-model="inputVal"
  :filter-method="filterMethod"
  collapse-tags
  :filterable="filterable"
  :disabled="disabled"
  clearable
  :size="size"
  :placeholder="placeholder"
  :multiple="multiple"
  @focus="focus"
>
  <el-option
    v-for="(option) in filterOptions"
    :key="option[opValue]"
    :label="formatOption(option)"
    :value="option[opValue]"
  />
</el-select>
